ftop<br />\n普通旅行唔係好方便咁做<br />\n仲有要影到佢個啲 要睇下你用咩鏡<br />\n我見仲有有個地點佢地個班成日去 東京仿九龍城寨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琦玉，好耐之前都有見過人介紹，多謝你勾返起個回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 我有follow啊，不過攝影師習慣都唔肯share個位置，所以就問下各位巴絲意見<br />\n<br />\n長知識！原來係用航拍，怪不得下下都咁既角度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  城寨樂園都放左係行程之內，因為對上樓梯個張相都係川崎，所以想到當地請教下，睇下會唔會搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49bec1fdbf5def1e0cf3a54e5141d1a58859877","tid":309191,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"佢地不嬲都唔share個location架<br />\n唔知你係咪初接觸<br />\n一向都係要hashtag location googlemap咁搵<br />\n基本上90%都會搵到既 真係唔得就要用個個地方嘅language搵"},{"pid":"7cf3026ce9d2abca9c18803fdf3e1eef7fd6b172","tid":309191,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實這趟東京之旅原定計劃係登富士山並影靚相，<br />\n但係暫時睇天氣預報，情況唔明朗<br />\n<br />\n所以想請教一下巴絲有無好意見，以備不時之需<br />\n主要係想食又平又好食既野同埋影相，購物都係其其次<br />\n<br />\n因為窮遊，希望各位的介紹都手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下圖片參考，方便各位給類似風格既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/041001_2ba4ba4bba0a95f99f3089851ce1d1fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F041001_2ba4ba4bba0a95f99f3089851ce1d1fd.jpg&h=5fa42e07&s={SIZE}\" /> 呢個地方好想搵到，暫時懷疑係川崎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/041052_eddf0f6a2d9699479ba5603530dedbf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F041052_eddf0f6a2d9699479ba5603530dedbf6.jpg&h=85830bd1&s={SIZE}\" /> 另外這種特別建築設計的地點</blockquote><br />\n是咪表參道 唔sure</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有聽人講過 但就係唔知確實位置 不過都多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces